00:21:10,040 --> 00:21:10,959
What are you doing?

321
00:21:12,319 --> 00:21:12,880
Lingzheng.

322
00:21:13,199 --> 00:21:14,959
How dare you use such a lowly trick

323
00:21:14,959 --> 00:21:15,719
