359
00:24:51,839 --> 00:24:53,479
Sir. Sorry, I'm late.

360
00:24:54,719 --> 00:24:55,599
Your wound...

361
00:24:57,000 --> 00:24:57,479
I'm fine.

362
00:24:59,160 --> 00:25:00,199
